---
title: Hoisin-Glazed Beef Burger with Sweet Potato Wedges and Spicy Mayo
description: Sweet and aromatic hoisin makes an exciting swap for traditional BBQ sauce. Cool and crunchy cucumbers, zesty green onions and wholesome spring mix are layered with a hearty beef patty for a fresh take on a burger supper!
